    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Titalaius <lb n="2"/>Sesti &amp;lt;f=S&amp;gt;ilius <lb n="3"/>civis <expan><abbr>Lingon</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Marti Men<lb break="no" n="5"/>obi et Litavi <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Votivtäfelchen in Form einer tabula ansata. Schreibtechnik: eingraviert. Unterhalb der Inschrift eine Triskele, flankiert von zwei hederae. (B): Barbet - Billerey - Joan: Z. 1: Titalatus.</p>
            </div>
